channel.title: SwiftSwitch Source
channel.description:
[size=5]SwiftSwitch Source[/size] [size=3]This is endless-hood v2 but i called it swiftswitch instead[/size]
Welcome... this is my 2nd release of a source hope you like this one.
If you read, downloaded, touched or even looked at this please reply
[u]Features[/u]
~New home ~New train ~New pkbox ~New starter ~New starter outfit ~Fully working range! ~Working login/logout ~Max stat = 99, not changed ~Tons of commands
[u]Commands[/u]
[b]Player commands[/b]
starter - Gives starter pack home - teleports you home Jad - Teleports you to the Jad Dragz - Teleports you to the dragz wc - Teleports you to wc'ing area kqueen - Teleports you to the kqueen cather - Teleports you to the fishing area 3rdage - teleports you to the 3rdage area pkbox - teleports you to the pkbox zammy - puts you on the zammy team slayer - teleports you to the slayer area dragpk - teleports you to the dragon pk area guilds - teleports you to the guild portal area shops - teleports you to the shops train - teleports you to train area teampk - teleports you to the team pk area skill - teleports you to the skill area mining - teleports you to the mining area mypk - shows you your pk stats gsmini - teleports you to the gs minigame suggest - suggests what you want to the hoster modinfo - brings up how to become mod+
[b]Mod commands[/b] + All above
sweet - gives you some [b]sweet[/b] armour god - makes you fly alert - alert the server modlook - gives you the server modlook Notedbarrows - gives you noted barrows az - teleports you the the staff zone sit - hmm lets take a seat.
[b]Admin commands[/b] + All above
pure - gives you pure stats master - gives you master stats xrichie - gives you max cash pickup - spawn an item banuser - ban someone deban - unban someone npc - spawn an npc pnpc - become an npc rich - gives you all rares tele - tele to some coords xteleto - tele to someone xteletome - tele someone to you xteleall - tele all to you
[b]Owner commands[/b] + All above
giveadmin - make some one an admin givemod - make some one a mod update - kick all from server for update demote - remove some one from staff fancy - ooh some fancy clothes cool - some cool clothes ipban - ipban someone pkzlook - gives you the pklook armour hide - become invisible show - become visible from invisible
[b]noarn command[/b] ( you need to be called noarn for this )
noarnlook - gives you noarns armour
[b]Swift command[/b] owner - explotion
AND MANY MORE COMMANDS
Some pics & vids
Working Range

Working login/logout
[img]http://i520.photobucket.com/albums/w328/ash-dude34/11-10-200815-07-46.png[/img]
Guild portals
[img]http://i520.photobucket.com/albums/w328/ash-dude34/11-10-200814-55-06.png[/img]
More portals
[img]http://i520.photobucket.com/albums/w328/ash-dude34/11-10-200814-48-46.png[/img]
slayer ( will be like rs in v3 )
[img]http://i520.photobucket.com/albums/w328/ash-dude34/11-10-200814-46-34.png[/img]
No more pics.. i will add some more soon...
CREDITS
60% Me - for coding 40% The Reaper - For Base
